1
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:16,208
- Congratulations, Your Highness!
- Congratulations, Your Highness!

2
00:00:16,240 --> 00:00:18,912
- Congratulations, Your Highness!
- Congratulations, Your Highness!

3
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,720
=Blossoms of Power=

4
00:02:57,728 --> 00:03:00,700
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

5
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:03,660
=Episode 21=

6
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:05,719
(East Palace)

7
00:03:05,719 --> 00:03:08,800
The auspicious hour has arrived!

8
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:28,599
Two hearts bound as
one with embroidered silk,

9
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:32,439
pearl and gem united,
enduring as sun and moon.

10
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:36,879
Gold-adorned saddle,
jade path leading to the throne,

11
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:40,599
may each step bring
peace through the years.

12
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:45,159
First scattering, fine grain
for a bountiful harvest.

13
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:49,800
Second scattering, beans and grains
for a lasting fortune and longevity.

14
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:53,759
Third scattering, rice and
millet fill a thousand halls.

15
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:57,960
May your household
always know abundance.

16
00:03:58,639 --> 00:04:00,400
May your bond last forever,

17
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,400
like twin blossoms on one stem.

18
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:05,520
May you know peace in every season.

19
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,199
First bow,

20
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,439
honor your parents' love and blessings.

21
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:16,399
May your union bring them joy.

22
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,879
Second bow,

23
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:24,839
may your hearts stay forever in harmony.

24
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,439
Share the ceremonial liquor.

25
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,959
To the Crown Princess,
of the Shen clan,

26
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:46,680
graceful in virtue
and noble in character.

27
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:51,600
Today, you are invested
as Crown Princess.

28
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:55,319
The ceremony is complete.
Let the banquet begin!

29
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,920
- Congratulations, Crown Prince.
- Congratulations, Crown Prince.

30
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,750
- Congratulations, Crown Princess.
- Congratulations, Crown Princess.

31
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,560
Your Highness.

32
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:20,079
His Highness had all
of this prepared for you.

33
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,584
He'll be dining with the guests,

34
00:05:21,632 --> 00:05:23,360
and he was worried you'd get hungry.

35
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:25,360
He said you may eat whatever you like

36
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,816
and ask for anything you need.

37
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,519
I'll take off this headdress first.

38
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,120
But...

39
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,680
You mustn't, Your Highness!

40
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,000
A bride's headdress

41
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,480
can only be removed by her husband.

42
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,800
Why are you back?

43
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,224
Weren't you joining the banquet?

44
00:05:44,399 --> 00:05:45,680
I knew you'd find it heavy

45
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,944
and you'd be uncomfortable.

46
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,279
Much better.

47
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,800
I'll come back early.

48
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:21,940
(East Palace)

49
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,279
You may all leave.

50
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,120
I thought

51
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,839
you wouldn't be back until late tonight.

52
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,399
But here you are,

53
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,759
not even four hours later.

54
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:56,399
All rules are relaxed on a wedding day.

55
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:59,480
Faced with their frail Crown Prince,

56
00:06:59,536 --> 00:07:01,664
the ministers could only
raise their cups and say,

57
00:07:01,750 --> 00:07:03,504
"Just drink what
you can, Your Highness."

58
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,040
I simply pretended
I was too weak to stay.

59
00:07:06,528 --> 00:07:07,630
Who would dare stop me?

60
00:07:19,904 --> 00:07:21,584
Your Highness, please behave yourself.

61
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:24,279
On our wedding night,
with my beautiful bride,

62
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,959
perhaps you could teach me

63
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,120
how to behave.

64
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,000
Let go of me!

65
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,560
Put me down!

66
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,639
We had an agreement.

67
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:39,380
One condition of this marriage
was that we wouldn't cross the line.

68
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,160
Don't be afraid.

69
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,040
I remember.

70
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,319
I'm taking you somewhere.

71
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,560
Where does this secret passage lead?

72
00:08:14,864 --> 00:08:16,070
You'll know when we get there.

73
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,560
Come, Youyou.

74
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,320
Xihe,

75
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:43,679
follow me.

76
00:09:34,399 --> 00:09:35,200
Father.

77
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:36,559
Brother.

78
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,240
Youyou.

79
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,519
Father.

80
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,279
Youyou.

81
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,559
My precious girl.

82
00:10:02,752 --> 00:10:04,150
My little girl is all grown up.

83
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,600
Now she's to become someone's wife.

84
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:12,440
Father, Brother,

85
00:10:13,088 --> 00:10:14,816
you left northwest without permission.

86
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,799
If the court finds out,
you could be in serious trouble.

87
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,399
Don't worry.

88
00:10:19,008 --> 00:10:20,270
I've taken care of everything.

89
00:10:20,608 --> 00:10:23,072
I knew you wanted your father
and brother here to see you off,

90
00:10:23,232 --> 00:10:24,600
but you put the greater good first

91
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:26,039
and never mentioned it to me.

92
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:27,720
I only wanted

93
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:29,360
to make that wish come true.

94
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,399
Your Highness,

95
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,559
you have my deepest gratitude.

96
00:10:37,919 --> 00:10:38,600
We're family now.

97
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:39,960
There's no need to thank me.

98
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,879
To be a son-in-law of our family,

99
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,264
if you didn't have this much
courage and responsibility,

100
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:47,200
I wouldn't feel safe
entrusting my sister to you.

101
00:10:48,100 --> 00:10:49,000
You're right, Brother.

102
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,639
Father.

103
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,639
Please accept my bow.

104
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,360
Father-in-law.

105
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,000
Please accept my bow as well.

106
00:11:09,070 --> 00:11:11,056
There are formalities
between ruler and subject.

107
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,240
Your Highness,

108
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,519
you mustn't bow to me like this.

109
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,799
Father-in-law,

110
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,670
here, we aren't ruler and subject.

111
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,000
We're family.

112
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:21,919
Now that I've married Youyou,

113
00:11:22,519 --> 00:11:23,600
her father

114
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,080
is naturally my father.

115
00:11:25,879 --> 00:11:26,919
And her brother

116
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,200
is my brother.

117
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:32,759
Father.

118
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:34,720
The first bow

119
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:38,399
is for giving me life and raising me.

120
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,279
The second bow

121
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,360
is for all the care and
guidance you've given me.

122
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,519
The third bow

123
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,679
is to bid you farewell.

124
00:11:58,256 --> 00:11:59,630
I might be someone's wife now,

125
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:02,080
but I'll remember

126
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:04,159
your teachings.

127
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,150
You've found a worthy husband,

128
00:12:15,824 --> 00:12:17,200
and it's an honor for our family.

129
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,750
May you build a happy home together

130
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,559
and grow old side by side.

131
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,519
Your Highness,

132
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,480
I entrust my precious daughter...

133
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:30,879
My Youyou

134
00:12:32,200 --> 00:12:33,399
to you.

135
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,639
So please,

136
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,720
respect her,

137
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,399
love her,

138
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,519
and protect her...

139
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,600
For the rest of your lives.

140
00:12:48,016 --> 00:12:49,744
Thank you for placing your trust in me.

141
00:12:50,944 --> 00:12:53,072
You have entrusted me
with your beloved daughter,

142
00:12:53,232 --> 00:12:54,550
and I'll treasure her always.

143
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,960
Xihe and I

144
00:12:58,879 --> 00:13:00,240
will stand by each other for life.

145
00:13:01,279 --> 00:13:02,519
Our love will endure.

146
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,120
Good.

147
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,720
Good.

148
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,399
Good.

149
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,440
Come.

150
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,759
I never would've guessed

151
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:05,559
you knew how to grill meat.

152
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,480
When I traveled in years past,

153
00:14:14,864 --> 00:14:16,736
I often had to make do
with what I could find.

154
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,440
Grilling was the easiest option.

155
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,720
The skin is crisp and golden,

156
00:14:46,279 --> 00:14:47,600
and the meat is tender and juicy.

157
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,519
It's cooked perfectly.

158
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:51,799
Have some more.

159
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,080
I really can't eat another bite.

160
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,039
Your Highness!

161
00:15:19,519 --> 00:15:20,799
Those are my chopsticks.

162
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,679
We're married now.

163
00:15:23,792 --> 00:15:25,472
There's no need to fuss over that.

164
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:27,759
How could you...

165
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,390
Don't you have any sense of propriety?

166
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,480
You're the Crown Prince.

167
00:15:31,879 --> 00:15:32,879
When I'm with you,

168
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:34,759
I'm just your husband.

169
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,279
Your Highness.

170
00:15:48,879 --> 00:15:50,360
I'm really happy today.

171
00:15:52,360 --> 00:15:53,840
Thank you for arranging everything

172
00:15:54,512 --> 00:15:56,416
so I could see my father and brother.

173
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,840
Youyou, if you're happy,

174
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,240
I'm even happier.

175
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:18,480
Father, Brother, please take care.

176
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:27,759
Though today,

177
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,960
I'm grateful to you,

178
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,799
I still ask that you

179
00:17:34,039 --> 00:17:35,640
keep our agreement in mind at all times.

180
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:49,680
Sharing a bed,

181
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,440
but not a pillow...

182
00:17:53,584 --> 00:17:54,688
I feel sorry for myself.

183
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,839
Would you care to explain

184
00:18:27,279 --> 00:18:28,519
where I was just lying?

185
00:18:32,119 --> 00:18:33,519
I don't know how

186
00:18:33,519 --> 00:18:34,920
you ended up in my arms either.

187
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:38,319
We were clearly far apart last night.

188
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:41,839
I know.

189
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,359
You must've been too tired,

190
00:18:44,432 --> 00:18:46,640
and sleeping on only half
the bed wasn't comfortable.

191
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:49,000
Perhaps we should sleep in
separate beds from now on.

192
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:50,839
No, no.

193
00:18:50,976 --> 00:18:52,048
That's not necessary.

194
00:18:52,528 --> 00:18:53,904
This bed is plenty big enough.

195
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,599
I promise, no matter how tired I am,

196
00:18:57,790 --> 00:18:59,040
I won't cross the line again.

197
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,519
Here, Du Huo.

198
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:30,839
Du Huo.

199
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:35,200
Your Highness!

200
00:19:35,350 --> 00:19:36,448
Get the medicine chest.

201
00:19:36,528 --> 00:19:37,472
Yes, Your Highness.

202
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,599
Let me see.

203
00:19:44,839 --> 00:19:45,680
Use this powder.

204
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,079
It's only a scratch.

205
00:19:52,352 --> 00:19:53,350
Don't worry about it.

206
00:19:53,599 --> 00:19:55,240
It could fester
if we don't treat it now.

207
00:19:55,799 --> 00:19:56,240
No need.

208
00:19:58,359 --> 00:19:58,799
No need.

209
00:20:03,039 --> 00:20:03,920
I'll do it.

210
00:20:12,599 --> 00:20:13,359
Does it hurt badly?

211
00:20:15,279 --> 00:20:16,680
Bring the cleansing balm.

212
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:17,920
Yes.

213
00:20:19,359 --> 00:20:20,640
That medicine is much gentler.

214
00:20:20,759 --> 00:20:22,720
It won't sting, even on an open wound.

215
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,790
It really doesn't hurt anymore.

216
00:20:54,839 --> 00:20:55,720
Tian Yuan,

217
00:20:56,079 --> 00:20:57,519
help me figure this out.

218
00:20:57,839 --> 00:20:59,720
What did I do wrong just now?

219
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:02,119
Why did His Highness glare at me?

220
00:21:04,119 --> 00:21:05,559
As trusted attendants,

221
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:07,559
sometimes we shouldn't be too capable.

222
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,440
Too capable?

223
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,599
Take what just happened.

224
00:21:11,072 --> 00:21:13,000
When Her Highness
asked if you had medicine,

225
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,440
you should've said,

226
00:21:14,519 --> 00:21:15,160
"No."

227
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,720
Then Her Highness

228
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:18,860
would have had more reason
to fuss over His Highness.

229
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,176
How do you not understand that?

230
00:22:46,359 --> 00:22:47,599
Your Highness.

231
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,720
May I have a word?

232
00:22:58,768 --> 00:23:00,000
Please, don't be so formal.

233
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:01,152
Go ahead, Grandfather.

234
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,119
I'm deeply honored by your regard,

235
00:23:04,519 --> 00:23:07,400
but I wouldn't presume to
call myself your grandfather.

236
00:23:07,759 --> 00:23:09,359
Still, there is one thing

237
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:12,680
I hope you'll forgive me for saying.

238
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:14,400
Please don't be so formal, Grandfather.

239
00:23:14,839 --> 00:23:16,319
Xihe and I are husband and wife.

240
00:23:16,340 --> 00:23:18,160
It's only right that I
honor you as my elder.

241
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:23,519
Your Highness,
you and Xihe are newlyweds,

242
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:28,640
but you should still
exercise some restraint.

243
00:23:32,799 --> 00:23:34,960
Yes. I'll remember
your advice, Grandfather.

244
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:36,500
I'll take my leave now.

245
00:23:43,980 --> 00:23:47,540
(Hanzhang Hall)

246
00:23:54,799 --> 00:23:55,480
Qing.

247
00:23:58,279 --> 00:23:59,480
Is today's meal

248
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,079
to your liking?

249
00:24:01,799 --> 00:24:02,920
It's rare that I get to dine

250
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,839
with you and Changying.

251
00:24:05,056 --> 00:24:06,816
Of course I have a good appetite.

252
00:24:16,759 --> 00:24:17,799
To be honest,

253
00:24:18,896 --> 00:24:21,070
ever since Shen Xihe
married to the Crown Prince,

254
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,599
I've been

255
00:24:23,119 --> 00:24:24,759
worried sick.

256
00:24:25,519 --> 00:24:27,119
Now that I can see you're alright,

257
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,039
as your mother,

258
00:24:29,759 --> 00:24:31,240
I can finally put my mind at ease.

259
00:24:44,599 --> 00:24:45,759
The wedding is over.

260
00:24:46,759 --> 00:24:48,240
The past is behind us now.

261
00:24:49,279 --> 00:24:50,519
If I still made you worry,

262
00:24:51,559 --> 00:24:52,799
I'd be an unfilial son.

263
00:24:54,599 --> 00:24:55,200
Mother,

264
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:56,759
a toast to you.

265
00:25:00,319 --> 00:25:00,799
Changying.

266
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:54,240
You look like you've
finally let go of the past.

267
00:25:55,039 --> 00:25:56,319
Even Mother believes that.

268
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,200
But I don't think

269
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,119
that's true.

270
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:13,880
Then tell me,

271
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,240
what am I really thinking?

272
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:19,720
You haven't let go.

273
00:26:24,279 --> 00:26:25,440
Neither have I.

274
00:26:28,208 --> 00:26:30,270
But Xihe and the Crown Prince
are married now.

275
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:31,960
We should wish her well

276
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,792
and hope everything
goes smoothly for her.

277
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,559
I'm going to keep Mother company.

278
00:26:53,599 --> 00:26:54,400
Changqing,

279
00:26:55,504 --> 00:26:57,030
I'll give you some time alone.

280
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:28,559
(Even if you've gained the upper hand,)

281
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,880
(your time is running out.)

282
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:33,039
(Xiao Huayong,)

283
00:27:33,799 --> 00:27:36,319
(I'll be waiting for the day
you breathe your last.)

284
00:27:49,079 --> 00:27:51,839
- Greetings, Father, Grandmother.
- Greetings, Father, Grandmother.

285
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:54,960
Rise.

286
00:27:58,960 --> 00:28:01,519
At last, I've heard Zhaoning

287
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:03,960
call me "Father."

288
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:07,759
It truly warms my heart.

289
00:28:08,559 --> 00:28:10,599
These gifts are from

290
00:28:10,599 --> 00:28:11,680
your grandmother and me.

291
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,200
We hope you

292
00:28:13,519 --> 00:28:17,000
will enjoy a lifetime of happiness
and blessings.

293
00:28:17,264 --> 00:28:20,400
- Thank you, Father and Grandmother.
- Thank you, Father and Grandmother.

294
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,559
Rise.

295
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:23,960
Seeing how devoted you
are to each other today

296
00:28:25,119 --> 00:28:26,599
puts my mind at ease.

297
00:28:28,039 --> 00:28:30,880
When Huayong lived outside the palace,

298
00:28:31,039 --> 00:28:33,839
the East Palace was so cold and empty.

299
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:36,839
Now that Zhaoning has moved in,

300
00:28:37,359 --> 00:28:38,599
and in time,

301
00:28:39,039 --> 00:28:41,519
we'll find you a few consorts

302
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:44,440
so you can give me
some great-grandchildren.

303
00:28:44,519 --> 00:28:47,519
Then the East Palace
will truly be lively.

304
00:28:48,359 --> 00:28:49,839
I don't want any consorts.

305
00:28:50,319 --> 00:28:51,200
Nonsense.

306
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:53,640
How can a Crown Prince have no consorts?

307
00:28:54,319 --> 00:28:56,279
Even before you married Zhaoning,

308
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:58,279
you had no consorts at all.

309
00:28:58,400 --> 00:28:59,839
That's unusual enough as it is.

310
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,000
Besides,

311
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:04,200
Zhaoning is new to the palace.

312
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:06,359
She may feel some unease.

313
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:09,359
Having sisters by her side
would be a comfort.

314
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:13,440
Plus, it's also for the sake
of continuing the royal line.

315
00:29:13,759 --> 00:29:16,480
This is a matter of state importance.

316
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,599
I've made a vow

317
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:22,359
to be with Xihe and no one else
for the rest of my life.

318
00:29:22,839 --> 00:29:23,680
Zhaoning,

319
00:29:24,119 --> 00:29:25,839
what do you think of this?

320
00:29:28,359 --> 00:29:30,480
I have no objections to this matter.

321
00:29:31,319 --> 00:29:34,160
I will follow the wishes
of His Highness and the elders.

322
00:29:53,008 --> 00:29:54,900
I'd like to take a walk
in the imperial garden.

323
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,512
Then I'll return to the palace first.

324
00:30:10,799 --> 00:30:13,000
Your Highness. About what
Empress Dowager said just now,

325
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:14,990
Crown Princess was
only pretending to be gracious

326
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:17,000
so no one would call her jealous.

327
00:30:17,319 --> 00:30:18,880
She must be against it deep down.

328
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,400
Please don't take her words to heart.

329
00:30:21,039 --> 00:30:22,440
Don't bother finding her excuse.

330
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,759
She truly doesn't care.

331
00:30:26,608 --> 00:30:27,310
How dare you!

332
00:30:27,799 --> 00:30:28,599
Who are you?

333
00:30:28,839 --> 00:30:30,599
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

334
00:30:30,799 --> 00:30:32,319
I accidentally fell

335
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,200
and caused you offense.

336
00:30:38,119 --> 00:30:39,440
Your Highness,

337
00:30:39,720 --> 00:30:40,640
could you

338
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:43,400
help me up?

339
00:30:51,840 --> 00:30:53,200
Your Highness!

340
00:30:53,744 --> 00:30:55,490
- Someone, come quickly!
- Your Highness!

341
00:30:55,504 --> 00:30:56,704
His Highness has fainted!

342
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:58,880
(East Palace)

343
00:30:58,880 --> 00:30:59,440
Your Highness.

344
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:02,150
That lady is the
Vice Minister of War's second daughter.

345
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,599
She's always been known
for her beauty. What she did today

346
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:07,056
was clearly meant to secure a
place as your consort.

347
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:08,960
But after you fainted,

348
00:31:08,976 --> 00:31:09,960
His Majesty was furious,

349
00:31:10,032 --> 00:31:11,824
and the Vice Minister of War
was reprimanded.

350
00:31:11,824 --> 00:31:13,160
The Empress Dowager even declared

351
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:15,240
that she was a lady of loose morals.

352
00:31:15,599 --> 00:31:17,200
From now on, any lady

353
00:31:17,359 --> 00:31:18,480
who dares make a move on you

354
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,039
will think twice.

355
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:36,960
Do you have no heart?

356
00:31:38,279 --> 00:31:39,799
I haven't done anything to you.

357
00:31:40,070 --> 00:31:42,144
Ladies are throwing
themselves at your husband,

358
00:31:42,279 --> 00:31:43,440
and you don't care at all?

359
00:31:44,799 --> 00:31:46,559
It's only natural for
you to take consorts.

360
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,000
I'll accept it calmly.

361
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:49,799
I won't get jealous.

362
00:31:51,319 --> 00:31:52,400
So to you,

363
00:31:52,759 --> 00:31:54,359
I don't really matter.

364
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,519
Of course, you matter.

365
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,200
But you're

366
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,759
a master at making
something out of nothing.

367
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,680
What's this?

368
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:28,319
You won't let me get close to you,

369
00:32:29,119 --> 00:32:30,400
so I can only draw you

370
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,920
to ease my longing.

371
00:32:33,759 --> 00:32:34,559
Perfect.

372
00:32:35,119 --> 00:32:36,880
Once you take a consort,

373
00:32:37,359 --> 00:32:38,839
you won't be so lonely anymore,

374
00:32:39,519 --> 00:32:41,880
and you won't need
drawings to satisfy yourself.

375
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,039
Your Highness.

376
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,839
Haven't you noticed

377
00:32:49,936 --> 00:32:52,144
Crown Princess has
been acting strangely lately?

378
00:32:52,519 --> 00:32:53,160
I have.

379
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:55,480
But I don't know why.

380
00:32:56,839 --> 00:32:58,440
Could it be because the Empress Dowager

381
00:32:58,440 --> 00:33:00,000
wanted you to take a consort,

382
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,799
and then other ladies
tried to seduce you?

383
00:33:03,079 --> 00:33:04,440
But I turned them all down.

384
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,559
Once a lady falls in love,

385
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,110
she stops being reasonable.

386
00:33:13,079 --> 00:33:14,920
This must be what they call jealousy.

387
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,759
The Crown Princess is jealous?

388
00:33:23,119 --> 00:33:24,279
I wouldn't dare dream of it.

389
00:34:04,759 --> 00:34:06,039
Greetings, Prince Lie.

390
00:34:06,256 --> 00:34:08,288
What are you doing here,
Young Lady Qingshu?

391
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:10,159
I came here specifically
to wait for you.

392
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,079
For me?

393
00:34:13,456 --> 00:34:14,848
Is something the matter?

394
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,039
I've heard

395
00:34:17,039 --> 00:34:19,280
of your exploits on the battlefield.

396
00:34:20,079 --> 00:34:22,079
You fought bravely and
struck fear into the enemy.

397
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:26,320
I've admired you for a long time.

398
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:27,760
May I ask

399
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,400
whether I might have the honor

400
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:31,559
of joining you for tea?

401
00:34:33,040 --> 00:34:34,630
I'm flattered, Young Lady Qingshu,

402
00:34:35,200 --> 00:34:36,656
but I don't feel the same way.

403
00:34:37,744 --> 00:34:39,488
I have matters to attend to at home.

404
00:34:39,920 --> 00:34:40,800
Please excuse me.

405
00:34:48,079 --> 00:34:48,880
Young Lady,

406
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,920
what are we going to do?

407
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,199
At this point,

408
00:34:53,679 --> 00:34:54,880
there's only one option left.

409
00:34:56,559 --> 00:34:59,199
His Majesty and the Empress Dowager
want Prince Ning to remarry,

410
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,880
and they have Hu Yingrao in mind.

411
00:35:01,072 --> 00:35:03,630
No wonder you've been visiting
the Hu residence so often lately

412
00:35:03,639 --> 00:35:05,239
and getting so close to Young Lady Hu.

413
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,336
And today, you even...

414
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:23,000
The Empress Dowager asked the
noble ladies to perform at this banquet

415
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,599
as a discreet way

416
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:26,720
for the princes to
choose prospective brides.

417
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:36,380
(Xiao Wenxi, Princess of Ruyang)

418
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,400
It's so hot.

419
00:36:03,320 --> 00:36:04,679
(That smells like verbena.)

420
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:16,880
Qingshu.

421
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,679
Take a look at my face.

422
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:20,039
It's so itchy.

423
00:36:20,039 --> 00:36:21,800
You've broken out in red spots.

424
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,000
Red spots?

425
00:36:24,559 --> 00:36:26,039
How did this happen all of a sudden?

426
00:36:26,559 --> 00:36:28,079
I'm about to perform.

427
00:36:30,079 --> 00:36:31,559
Come with me. I'll help you fix it.

428
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,480
I have a way.

429
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:56,480
Watch out!

430
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:58,639
Young Lady Hu!

431
00:36:58,960 --> 00:36:59,800
Assassin!

432
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:00,599
Your Majesty.

433
00:37:00,679 --> 00:37:01,840
I failed in my duty.

434
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:03,199
I thought

435
00:37:03,719 --> 00:37:05,519
the Crown Princess was
exceptionally capable.

436
00:37:05,719 --> 00:37:08,480
That's why I entrusted
this blessing ceremony to her.

437
00:37:08,599 --> 00:37:10,480
Yet such a suspicious
incident has occurred.

438
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:12,679
Your Majesty,
please mete out strict punishment.

439
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:21,170
♪I've hidden so many words♪

440
00:37:21,790 --> 00:37:24,590
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

441
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:32,430
♪So never uncover♪

442
00:37:32,620 --> 00:37:34,980
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

443
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:38,840
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

444
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:45,140
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

445
00:37:46,900 --> 00:37:49,720
♪Every answer I gave♪

446
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:53,370
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

447
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:57,530
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

448
00:37:57,790 --> 00:38:01,100
♪How hard it truly was?♪

449
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:07,510
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

450
00:38:08,500 --> 00:38:10,830
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

451
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:17,860
♪Pretending to be brave
as if I'd never been hurt♪

452
00:38:19,270 --> 00:38:22,400
♪It's a shame I never could♪

453
00:38:22,850 --> 00:38:25,860
♪Give you a moon in return♪

454
00:38:25,970 --> 00:38:32,610
♪With the same open heart you loved me♪

455
00:38:32,610 --> 00:38:36,280
♪I've crossed the wasteland of memories♪

456
00:38:37,150 --> 00:38:39,910
♪Never knowing I was lost♪

457
00:38:40,350 --> 00:38:43,480
♪Why don't you take me away?♪

458
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:49,870
♪Lead me out of this endless game
of hide-and-seek♪

459
00:38:51,270 --> 00:38:54,820
♪You'll never♪

460
00:38:55,100 --> 00:39:04,570
♪Know how much I long to, long to♪

461
00:39:30,740 --> 00:39:34,220
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this film)

